      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision! While it\u2019s currently in poor condition and will require some significant mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC, it serves as a great foundation for a restoration enthusiast or anyone looking for a budget-friendly way to get a classic model. It\u2019s an honest start for your next big garage project!",
