    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior presents well with a nice shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it remains strong and drives exactly as it should, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver or a great project car for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is functional, though the upholstery shows significant wear and there is a tear in the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need some suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to bring it back to peak performance. It\u2019s an honest car at an honest price for someone looking for affordable transportation.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
